                    <span>This is a good book telling the philosophy behind RUP. And it also gives some practical advice to adopt, config and apply RUP.Although it is not a thorough description of RUP because it doesn't systematicly describe the disciplines in RUP, it provides some other reference. A good book for RUP beginners.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent book for RUP beginners</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
